IMAPAccount nxtbook
Host imap.gmail.com
User neagleson@nxtbookmedia.com
PassCmd "offlineimap.py neagleson@nxtbookmedia.com imap.gmail.com"
AuthMechs LOGIN
SSLType IMAPS
SSLVersions TLSv1
# On OS X, if OpenSSL has been installed by homebrew, there's a CA cert at this
# path: http://stackoverflow.com/a/28274272/1128957
CertificateFile /usr/local/etc/openssl/cert.pem


IMAPStore nxtbook-remote
Account nxtbook

MaildirStore nxtbook-local
Path ~/mail/nxtbook/
Inbox ~/mail/nxtbook/Inbox

Channel nxtbook
Master :nxtbook-remote:
Slave :nxtbook-local:
Patterns *
Create Both
SyncState *
